iraa","tag-charity-al-sadaqah","tag-companions-sahaba","tag-gold-al-dhahab","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-manners-adab","tag-mountains","tag-prophetic-virtues-manaqib-nabawi","tag-spending"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-5bW","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":11519,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/18\/do-not-curse-insult-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19960,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Do not curse companions of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not insult my companions. If one of you were to spend the likes of mount Uhud in gold, it would not reach a small portion of theirs or even half of that.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3673,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34484,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/20\/sadaqah-allah-multiplies-uhud\/","url_meta":{"origin":19960,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Allah multiplies charity until it is like a mountain","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 20, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah will raise up a date or a morsel in charity, just as one of you raises his mare or his young, until it becomes like the mountain of Uhud.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 3317 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&