ory\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35794,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/26\/allah-never-wrong\/","url_meta":{"origin":19960,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: Allah can never be unjust to His servants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf Allah were to punish the inhabitants of His heavens and His earth, He would punish them without being unjust to them. If He were to have mercy on them, His mercy is better for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8039,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/bad-neighbors-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19960,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: How many bad neighbors on Judgment Day?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHow many neighbors will be brought with their neighbors on the Day of Resurrection? One will say: O Lord, this man closed his door to me and refused to show courtesy!\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 111\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19960","tar